msgid "Don't write parts of the query that you don't need: write `Person.find(\"order by name\")` or `Person.find(\"name = ?1 and status = ?2\", \"stef\", Status.Alive)` or even better `Person.find(\"name\", \"stef\")`."
msgstr "No escribas partes de la consulta que no necesites: escribe `Person.find(\"order by name\")` o `Person.find(\"name = ?1 and status = ?2\", \"stef\", Status.Alive)` o incluso mejor `Person.find(\"name\", \"stef\")`."

